{"id": 5685, "title": "Ticket #5685: Don't build VOMS if not building Globus", "description": "<blockquote>\nOur cmake build scripts attempt to build VOMS even if the user disabled Globus support.  This <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www-auth.cs.wisc.edu/lists/htcondor-users/2016-May/msg00067.shtml\">has tripped up folks attempting to build HTCondor</a>.\n\n<p>Patch HTCondor so if Globus is disabled, don't bother with VOMS.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2016-May-23 16:15:31 by tannenba:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>CODE REVIEW</strong>\n\n<p>Code reviewed by Jaime, who happened to be sitting next to me....</p></blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-May-23 16:13</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/07eb4607aa6307786b32f63b02879eafc589ce4a\">[48400]</a></span>: Don't build VOMS if not building Globus. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5685\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5685'); return false;\" title=\"Don't build VOMS if not building Globus\">#5685</a></span>  (By Todd Tannenbaum )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "defect", "last_change": "2016-May-23 16:15", "status": "resolved", "created": "2016-May-23 16:11", "fixed_version": "2016-May-23 16:11", "broken_version": "v080200", "priority": "3", "subsystem": "Packaging", "assigned_to": "tannenba", "derived_from": "", "creator": "tannenba", "rust": "", "customer_group": "users", "visibility": "public", "notify": "", "due_date": ""}